    "long_instructions": "## Gift Recommendations, Part 2\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to get gift recommendations for your friend.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Try the provided prompt first** by copying and pasting it into AI Chat: \r\n\r\n>Give me 3 gift ideas under $30 for a 15-year-old girl who likes watercolor paintings. Her favorite birthday gift last year was a purple Polaroid camera.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read **AI Chat's response**.\r\n4. **Now, modify the prompt** to make it about someone you know. Change details like **age, interests, or past gifts** to see how AI adapts its recommendations.\r\n5. Press **Send** again and compare the response to the original.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n",
